uye vanhu vakatotanga kutora mari kubva kuma akaudhi ake emu bhengi.

0:15:53.760,0:16:00.500
Unoreva hanzvadzi, kuti kuedza kwose kwakaitwa kukumisa kuti usvike pa SCOAN - ndizvo here?

0:16:00.500,0:16:01.760
Hongu.

0:16:01.760,0:16:07.420
Izvi zvakanyatsosimbisa izvo munhu wa Mwari akataura kuti kana waita chisarudzo chekuuya ku SCOAN

0:16:07.420,0:16:11.280
tinoziva kuti chinhu chipi nechipi chiri pedyo na Jesu chinosangana ne kurwiswa.

0:16:11.280,0:16:15.760
Ndiko kurwisa uko hanzvadzi yedu yakasanga nako asati asvika pano.

0:16:15.760,0:16:21.680
Madhamu, tiudzei, parwendo urwu rwekuya pano, pamakanga muri mundege, munogona here kutsanangura kwatiri zvakaitika?

0:16:21.680,0:16:36.760
Mundege, ndakatanga kusanzwa zvakanaka saka ndakatanga kunyengetera ne kuverenga Pisarema 51 katatu.

0:16:36.760,0:16:46.740
Ndakaudza mukadzi aive agere pedyo neni, "Ndege iyi haisi kuzomhara zvakanaka." Ndapota, iwe unogona kunyengetera here? "

0:16:46.740,0:16:48.420
Akati, "Ndiri kunyengetera".

0:16:48.420,0:16:54.820
Ndakati, "Kwete. Handina kuona muromo wako uchinyengetera".

0:16:54.820,0:16:57.880
Ndaingotambura.

0:16:57.880,0:17:05.540
Kwemaminitsi anenge 30 kusvika ku35, ndege yacho yakanga isingagoni kumhara.

0:17:05.540,0:17:11.000
Ndege yacho yakadzika ndokukwira kakawanda.

0:17:11.000,0:17:22.120
Apo ndege yakazosvika ku nhandare yendege, yakamhara sekunge yaiva yavekubva payaifanira ku mharira.

0:17:22.120,0:17:27.680
Tinovonga Mwari nokuti dai yakanga isiri minyengetero

0:17:27.680,0:17:32.860
uye minyengetero ye mu Porofita T.B. Joshua, hatizivi kuti taizova kupi.

0:17:32.860,0:17:35.040
Ndinotarisira kuti tiri kuteerera izvo hanzvadzi yedu iri kutaura.

0:17:35.040,0:17:40.180
Ichi chaiva chiitiko apo akanyatsofamba panyama achiuya ku SCOAN.

0:17:40.180,0:17:45.640
Takaona pane vhidhiyo kare kuti dhimoni raive mukati mehanzvadzi yedu rairerurura sei zvarakanga raronga

0:17:45.640,0:17:52.120
kukonzera njodzi yakakomba zvikuru ne ndege, iyo yaive chaizvoizvo ichiunza mazana evashanyi

0:17:52.120,0:17:55.060
pano pa SCOAN kubva kunyika dzakasiyana.

0:17:55.060,0:17:59.020
Asi kubwinya ngakuve kuna Mwari wa Masimba Ose kuti hanzvadzi yedu iri pakati pedu.

0:17:59.020,0:18:02.040
Akadzikinurwa zvachose kubva pamweya wakaipa iwoyo.

0:18:02.040,0:18:06.980
Zvino, hanzvadzi, apo iwe wakasvika panyama pa SCOAN ukasvika pachechi -

0:18:06.980,0:18:09.160
unogona here kutsanangura zvakaitika?

0:18:09.160,0:18:20.300
Ndisati ndauya pano, ndakanyengetera kuti ndisati ndapinda muimba yechechi, ndaida kupfugama

0:18:20.300,0:18:28.280
ne kuteerera Mwari we mu Porofita T.B. Joshua nokuda kwezvandakaona pa Emmanuel TV.

0:18:28.280,0:18:33.460
Ndizvo zvandakaita asi shure kwe izvozvo, ndakanga ndisingagoni kurangarira zvaiitika.

0:18:33.460,0:18:38.720
Chinhu chekupedzisira chaunoyeuka ndeche kupfugama pasi kuti unyengetere apo wakasvika muchechi

0:18:38.720,0:18:42.240
asi shure kweizvozvo ... haugoni kuyeuka zvakazoitika?

0:18:42.240,0:18:42.880
Hongu.

0:18:42.880,0:18:48.320
Zvose zvataona pa vhidhiyo, zvatiri kuona iye zvino,iko kuratidzira, kureurura kwedhimoni iroro,

0:18:48.320,0:18:51.100
iwe wakanga usingazivi zvaiitika panguva iyoyo?

0:18:51.100,0:18:53.240
Kwete zvachose.

0:18:53.240,0:18:58.240
Hama, tinogona kuona kuti zvechokwadi uku kwaiva kudzikinurwa kwemweya kwaitika

0:18:58.240,0:19:04.220
uye hanzvadzi yedu yaitambudzwa nedhimoni iro raive nechinangwa chekumushandisa kuti aparadze zvakanyanya,

0:19:04.220,0:19:09.440
kwete muhupenyu hwake bedzi asi ne hupenyu hwemazana ayo akauya ku SCOAN.

0:19:09.440,0:19:15.400
Asi ne kubwinya kwa Mwari mweya iwoyo wakakundwa uye nhasi hanzvadzi yedu iri pakati pedu.

0:19:15.400,0:19:21.020
Hanzvadzi, tinoziva kuti mushure mekusangana uko apo mweya wakaipa iwowo wakafumurwa ne kusungwa,

0:19:21.020,0:19:23.580
musi we Svondo apo Prophet T.B. Joshua akakunyengeterera.

0:19:23.580,0:19:28.840
Tiudze; Kubvira panguva iyoyo, chii chachinja chaunonyatsoona mu upenyu hwako

0:19:28.840,0:19:33.560
Ndine rugare mumwoyo mangu.

0:19:33.560,0:19:42.740
Ndaishandisa mishonga yechirwere cheshuga asi kubvira pandakauya pano, ndaigona kudya mupunga ndisinganzwe chinhu.

0:19:42.740,0:19:46.060
Ndakasimba. Ndinotenda Mwari.

0:19:46.060,0:19:48.820
Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Jesu Kristu!

0:19:48.840,0:19:52.300
Nguva ye Uchapupu

0:19:52.300,0:19:54.260
Ndinoda kuimba rwiyo.

0:19:54.260,0:20:00.680
Zvakanaka, musati maimba rwiyo madhamu, mati kare maive nezviroto zvinotyisa muchiona nyoka,

0:20:00.680,0:20:02.680
zvipembenene zvakasiyana, mhuka ...

0:20:02.680,0:20:05.720
Kubva pamakasvika pano mange muchirara sei?

0:20:05.720,0:20:10.680
Ndinorara zvakanaka semucheche.

0:20:10.680,0:20:15.820
Ameni. Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Jesu Kristu.

0:20:15.820,0:20:21.100
Tanzwa kubva kune hanzvadzi yedu pano; panyama utano hwake hwakadzorerwa.

0:20:21.100,0:20:25.700
Takanzwa dhimoni raireurura kuti rakakonzera zvirwere zvakawanda mumuviri wake.

0:20:25.700,0:20:29.380
Asi ati sezvo iye asvika pano ave ne hutano hwakanaka kudya chero rudzi rwese rwe chekudya,

0:20:29.380,0:20:31.820
asingatore mishonga yaimbove achivimba nayo

0:20:31.820,0:20:36.760
Uye mumweya zvakare, iye ane rugare mumwoyo make, uye ange achirara zvakanaka,

0:20:36.760,0:20:38.360
mbiri kuna Mwari wa Masimbaose.

0:20:38.360,0:20:43.980
Madhamu, tinoziva imi pachenyu; mangopinda muchechi dzikiniro yenyu ichibva yaitika.

0:20:43.980,0:20:50.660
Ndeapi mashoko enyu emazano kune vatariri vedu pasi rose uye avo varipo pano?

0:20:50.660,0:20:56.460
Kana iwe usingakwanisi kuuya pano, unogona kubata sikirini ye Emmanuel TV kumba

0:20:56.460,0:21:02.400
Ingoisa kutenda kwako muna Jesu Kristu uye Achabvisa matambudziko ako ose.

0:21:02.400,0:21:03.340
Ndinotenda Ishe.

0:21:03.340,0:21:07.800
Ameni. Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Jesu Kristu!

